    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Hello Experts,&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;I want to use the Country Spec Enhance in the Business Partner Master Data Management app (F3163), but there is no item.&lt;BR /&gt;In the Maintain Business Partner app, there is a tab as General Data of Supplier role.&lt;BR /&gt;It wasn't in the F3163 app.&lt;BR /&gt;Regarding Japanese Country/Region-Specific Functions, SAP Help has instructions for using the Maintain Business Partner app, but can't I manage it with the F3163 app?&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;A href="https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_S4HANA_CLOUD/b8c08e0197454541a11f8d46ef1ab96e/6bc580003a424a43a5abbae28ed4fb3b.html?locale=en-US" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_S4HANA_CLOUD/b8c08e0197454541a11f8d46ef1ab96e/6bc580003a424a43a5abbae28ed4fb3b.html?locale=en-US&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ryofujishiro_0-1730456903641.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/185894i2407E7748DC70975/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ryofujishiro_0-1730456903641.png" alt="ryofujishiro_0-1730456903641.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Above figure shows where Vender:Country-Spec.Enh are existing.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ryofujishiro_1-1730457243698.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/185897i642B8AB1DA1E10E0/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ryofujishiro_1-1730457243698.png" alt="ryofujishiro_1-1730457243698.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Above figure is where I am looking for in the Business Partner Master Data Management app(Role:Supplier). Vender : Country-Spec.Enh. are not here.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;I checked adapt UI if these field are hidden but I couldn't find there neither.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
