    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/ps/qaq-p/13929602</id>
    <title>ps</title>
    <updated>2024-11-06T03:38:41.988000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>ITTS_Julia</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1574232</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;想請問&lt;SPAN&gt;Publice cloud&lt;/SPAN&gt;是否可以直接銷售出貨專案庫存&lt;SPAN&gt;(601+Q)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;情境為採購入庫時，存貨入到專案庫存&lt;SPAN&gt;(Q)&lt;/SPAN&gt;，直接銷售此專案庫存&lt;SPAN&gt;(Q)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;步驟&lt;SPAN&gt;:&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;OL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;採購單&lt;SPAN&gt;(&lt;/SPAN&gt;有維護專案號碼&lt;SPAN&gt;)&lt;/SPAN&gt;入庫時，存貨入到專案庫存&lt;SPAN&gt;(Q)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;開立銷售訂單&lt;SPAN&gt;SO&amp;amp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;出貨單&lt;SPAN&gt;DN&lt;/SPAN&gt;，銷售訂單上有維護專案號碼&lt;SPAN&gt;(WBS)&lt;/SPAN&gt;，開立出貨單，出貨單也有專案號碼&lt;SPAN&gt;(WBS)&lt;/SPAN&gt;，但是發貨過帳時，系統只允許出未限制庫存(601)&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;IMG&lt;/SPAN&gt;的&lt;SPAN&gt;ITEM CATEGORY&lt;/SPAN&gt;在&lt;SPAN&gt;PUBLIC CLOUD&lt;/SPAN&gt;無法調整，所以也無法調整&lt;SPAN&gt;Special stock-Q&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/OL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;4.&lt;/SPAN&gt;查看&lt;SPAN&gt;Scope:6GD - Engineer Products and Systems - Project with Production&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;但此&lt;SPAN&gt;scope &lt;/SPAN&gt;銷售訂單出貨是出貨未限制庫存&lt;SPAN&gt;(601)&lt;/SPAN&gt;，非銷售專案庫存。&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ITTS_Julia_0-1730860247455.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187243i7EA3D8904DEE399C/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ITTS_Julia_0-1730860247455.png" alt="ITTS_Julia_0-1730860247455.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ITTS_Julia_1-1730860276697.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187244iE9305E2BED1DA64B/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ITTS_Julia_1-1730860276697.png" alt="ITTS_Julia_1-1730860276697.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;出貨單，如下，有維護專案號碼&lt;SPAN&gt;(WBS)&lt;/SPAN&gt;，但是代碼為&lt;SPAN&gt;601&lt;/SPAN&gt;，而不是&lt;SPAN&gt;601+Q&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ITTS_Julia_2-1730860313282.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187245i9C4E8622A3296F15/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ITTS_Julia_2-1730860313282.png" alt="ITTS_Julia_2-1730860313282.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ITTS_Julia_3-1730860396048.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187246i0FE84BD0D5C0EAC1/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ITTS_Julia_3-1730860396048.png" alt="ITTS_Julia_3-1730860396048.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ITTS_Julia_4-1730860428645.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187247i7D88F6C6D6061F90/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ITTS_Julia_4-1730860428645.png" alt="ITTS_Julia_4-1730860428645.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;目前此料有庫存於專案庫存&lt;SPAN&gt;(Q)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ITTS_Julia_5-1730860530033.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187248iE1B6C3CC6D182152/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ITTS_Julia_5-1730860530033.png" alt="ITTS_Julia_5-1730860530033.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;ITEM CATEGORY&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ITTS_Julia_6-1730860586338.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187249iF280B522C7A303DC/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ITTS_Julia_6-1730860586338.png" alt="ITTS_Julia_6-1730860586338.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/ps/qaq-p/13929602"/>
    <published>2024-11-06T03:38:41.988000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
